0.75.name: wordpress/tilt-social-share-widget
0.75.description:
Tilt Social Share Widget is a simple widget that allows you to enable sharing of your posts and/or pages.

Available Services

With Tilt Social Share Widget you can activate the following sharing services:

  • Del.icio.us
  • Designbump
  • Digg
  • Diigo
  • Evernote
  • Facebook
  • Friendfeed
  • Google+
  • Google Bookmarks
  • Google Buzz
  • LinkedIn
  • Newsvine
  • Ping.fm
  • Pinterest
  • Posterous
  • Reddit
  • Slashdot
  • StumbleUpon
  • Technorati
  • Tumblr
  • Twitter
  • Yahoo Bookmarks

More Information

To know more about Tilt Social Share Widget go to xonoxlabs.com
